30 (2) The Commission shall hold the public hearing jointly with the
31 governing body of the county or municipal corporation in which any portion of the
32 construction of the generating station, overhead transmission line, [or] qualified generator
33 lead line, OR ENERGY STORAGE DEVICE is proposed to be located, unless the governing
34 body declines to participate in the hearing.

